<h2 align="left" style="color:blue"> Whole Life Cover - 99 Years </h2><br><h4 align="left">Option to get cover for a limited period or for your entire<br> lifetime of up to 99 years.</h4>
<h2 align="left" style="color:blue">Return of Total Premiums </h2><br><h4 align="left">Option to get return of total premiums paid at the end of the <br>policy term in case of no claim.</h4>
<h2 align="left" style="color:blue">Waiver of Premiums	</h2><br><h4 align="left">No future premiums shall be payable if diagnosed with covered <br>Critical Illness or on occurrence of Accidental Total and Permanent Disability.</h4>
<h2 align="left" style="color:blue">Critical3 + Terminal Illness Cover	</h2><br><h4 align="left">Option to augment cover with accelerated Terminal Illness<br> or additional Critical Illness cover.</h4>

<h2 align="right" style="color:blue">Limited Premium Pay </h2><br><h4 align="right">Option to choose your premium payment term Choose to pay<br> premiums every year of the policy term, for first 5/10/15/20/25 years<br> or up to age 60 Years,<br> or just once for the entire policy term.</h4>
<h2 align="right" style="color:blue">Increasing Cover Option </h2><br><h4 align="right">Sum Assured increases by 10% per annum (simple interest) after <br>completion of every Policy Year, provided the Policy is in-force.</h4>
<h2 align="right" style="color:blue">Special Exit Value </h2><br><h4 align="right">Sum Assured increases by 10% per annum (simple interest) after<br> completion of every Policy Year, provided the Policy is in-force.</h4>
<h2 align="right" style="color:blue">Steady Income Benefit2	</h2><br><h4 align="right">A monthly survival income equal to 0.1% of Sum Assured <br>at inception will be payable from the time of attaining 60 years<br> of age till the earlier of death or end of Policy Term.</h4>


